    rdfs:label "Employment Records Protocol" ;
    rdfs:comment "Protocol reference for the Employment Record data model. Informed by International Labour Organization (ILO) conventions on employment documentation, the International Standard Classification of Occupations (ISCO-08), and national labor records management frameworks." ;
